    <note>Li(3) Furen(7) [5230] Zheng Xie, WJ, 22.4a-7b. According to Zheng(1) Xie [13378], her ancestry--father, Zhouxun [20034], grandfather, Ding(5) [20033], and great grandfather, Jing(5) [20032] (all had civil offices)--was very distinguished and usually intermarried with elite families (gui). We cannot identify her family. The ancestry of Zhao(1) Kejie's [20035] wife was exactly the same except that the generation for Jing(5) and Ding(5) are reversed. They are identified as Wen people, but Wen is not an administrative unit, but does probably refer to the area around a river in central Shandong. CBD, 5, 3822.</note>
